message.body: What's the final college decision!? Also, did you actually have your birthday party in April? If so, sorry I missed it. We should hang out soon. Like forreals this time. School gets out so early this year!

Wessssss mothafuckas! Haha yayyy! :) And no I actually never had a birthday party!!! :'( There was so much life stuff happening around my bday which made it mad complicated. Def def def! We gotta hang!!
Haha woohoo! Wes is awesome. Yeah I get that, we should have a belated birthday party for you during regents week!
Yeah I was considering a belated bday party but thought it was obnoxious..? Idk people are telling me I should have one! Eee
You should! Or a combined belated bday party + core pre-college hangout
Def def! Core needs to hang out at least 2 or 3 more times before college!
